@name wish-fizzbuzz
@version 1.0.0

Print the numbers from 1 to 100, one per line, with these substitutions:
- If the number is divisible by both 3 and 5, print "FizzBuzz" instead.
- If the number is divisible by only 3, print "Fizz" instead.
- If the number is divisible by only 5, print "Buzz" instead.
- Otherwise, print the number itself.
